# Kiro skill artifacts (code-review, refactor, steering-maintenance, judgement)
**/.code-review/
**/.judgement/
**/.refactor/
**/.steering-maintenance/

# Local env file for compose interpolation (keeps API keys out of git)
.env
*.env

# Bind-mounted runtime config from the compose example (generated config.yaml
# can hold API keys; state/feed/reports are runtime data) — never commit it
/config/

# go.work / go.work.sum are local-dev only (never committed)
go.work
go.work.sum
